---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
permalink: /
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
---
<div class="home-content">
  <header class="home-header">
    <h1>William Zujkowski</h1>
    <p>Software Engineer & Technology Enthusiast</p>
  </header>

  <div class="terminal-box">
    <div class="terminal-header">user@system: ~/profile</div>
    <div class="terminal-content">
      <div class="command-line">
        <span class="prompt">$</span>
        <span class="command">whoami</span>
      </div>
      <div class="response">
        <p>I'm a software engineer specializing in cloud architecture, cybersecurity, and AI/ML applications. With experience across the full development lifecycle, I build robust, scalable solutions that solve complex problems.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="command-line">
        <span class="prompt">$</span>
        <span class="command">skills --list</span>
      </div>
      <div class="response">
        <ul>
          <li>Cloud Architecture & DevOps</li>
          <li>Cybersecurity & Threat Analysis</li>
          <li>Machine Learning & AI Development</li>
          <li>Full Stack Development</li>
          <li>System Design & Architecture</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="command-line">
        <span class="prompt">$</span>
        <span class="command">cat interests.txt</span>
      </div>
      <div class="response">
        <p>When not coding, I enjoy exploring emerging technologies, contributing to open-source projects, and writing about tech trends. I'm particularly interested in the intersection of AI ethics, privacy, and security.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="recent-posts">
    <h2>Recent Blog Posts</h2>
    <ul class="post-list">
      {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse -%}
        {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
          <li class="post-item">
            <h3 class="post-title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <time class="post-date" datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            <div class="post-excerpt">
              <p>{{ post.data.description or post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(150) }}</p>
            </div>
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</a>
          </li>
        {% endif %}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>
    <p><a href="/blog/">View all posts &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
</div>